window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I would sell my dragon soul to possess her....</b></p> <p>From the moment I saw her, she held me enthralled. It was more than her beauty. It was in the very way she looked at the world. The way she looked at <i>me</i>.</p> <p>She saw me as no one ever had. The scars I tried to bury, the wounds no one else knew about. She saw the worst parts of meâ€”and she didn't look away.</p> <p>Together we pursue a shared nemesis. While a terrifying foe stalks us at every turn. Whatever enemy dares to get close, I will slay. Whatever path she walks, I will be beside her.</p> <p>For I am hers. Utterly. Completely. She's my greatest temptation. The other half of my soul. My mate.</p> <p><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>USA Today</i></b><b> bestselling author Donna Grant delivers a powerful story of redemption, danger, and passion in the next chapter of the Dragon Kings series.</b></p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
